data.description: Are you looking for a horse property? Look at this gem.  21 acres 6 different large horse paddocks and room for more. Nice 3 bedroom 2 bath home. Work shop and detach garage that has been used as a man cave. There is a second home on the property that could be bought also. Paved road just outside of Shawnee.
